A pupil was stabbed to death in classroom by another pupil in
Malebogo  outside Seshego.Police spokesperson Colonel Moatshe Ngoepe said one of the
pupils stabbed the other with a sharp instrument.He said  the dead pupil
was immediately taken to the local clinic where he was certified dead on
